            <title>[LU-14409] ldiskfs support for SUSE 15 SP2 5.3.18-24.46.1 kernel</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14409</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;SUSE 15 SP2 5.3.18-24.46.1 kernel includes:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Linux-commit: ef84c07364211bb4e398a9de45d1c13a32059cee&lt;br/&gt;
ext4: fix bogus warning in ext4_update_dx_flag()&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This breaks the pdirop patch which disables ext4_update_dx_flag.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Update the patch and update the configure test to selected&lt;br/&gt;
the correct series for SUSE kernels with this patch applied.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
